ActNational Capital Act
SubjectNational Capital Commission ** Granting Renewal - Mental Health Commission of Canada **
PrecisOrder authorizing the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to grant the option to extend for five years, commencing on January 1, 2016, the existing five-year lease with the MENTAL HEALTH COMMISSION OF CANADA in order to occupy office spaces in units 501 and 600 on the premises located at 96-100 Sparks Street in Ottawa.
